.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, pop, electronic
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, cherry, cucumber, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, camping, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, mystery, scientific, sports
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, horse, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, snowboarding, swimming
4 different games are played: monopoly, poker, backgammon, billiard
 1. the fan of electronic is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the fan of pop is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person playing poker##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person eating blueberry is between the person playing backgammon and the person eating cucumber##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
15. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Music-Genre      | electronic | dubstep     | blues        | pop      |
